            <span class="b2-hero-badge">현재 보기 · ${_curViewMeta.label}</span>
            <span class="b2-hero-badge">표시 스트리머 ${visPlayers.length}명</span>
            <span class="b2-hero-badge">대학 ${univList.length}곳</span>
